1. *Mnom* je povjeren zadatak da planiram sastanak. (I was entrusted with the task of planning the meeting.)
2. Ovi zadaci su za *mnom* već završeni. (These tasks are already finished by me.)
3. On je potpuno zanemario *mnom* date upute. (He completely ignored the instructions given by me.)
4. Ona se nije obratila *mnom* povodom informacija. (She did not contact me about the information.)
5. Očekuje se da ću *mnom* procjeniti situaciju. (It is expected that I will assess the situation by myself.)